1
00:00:18,390 --> 00:00:20,590
I didn't expect this war to last so long.

2
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:23,510
Does His Highness really plan
to enter peace talks?

3
00:00:23,510 --> 00:00:25,570
Will there really be peace from now on?

4
00:00:25,570 --> 00:00:26,870
Why aren't we fighting?

5
00:00:26,870 --> 00:00:28,280
The Monument of Loyalty was just erected.

6
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:29,230
In the battle of Jiuzhang Plain,

7
00:00:29,230 --> 00:00:29,920
we clearly won.

8
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:30,670
Runheng?

9
00:00:32,750 --> 00:00:33,280
Yuanji.

10
00:00:33,670 --> 00:00:34,530
Here they come.

11
00:00:37,110 --> 00:00:37,970
Here they come.

12
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:39,680
They're here.

13
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:48,170
Young Lord Xiao.

14
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,710
I hope you have been well

15
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:50,830
[Mu Lianyu, Eagle King]

16
00:00:50,030 --> 00:00:52,090
since our parting at Jiuzhang Plain.

17
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:55,030
Eagle King, you have come a long way
for the peace talks.

18
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:56,830
It must have been a hard journey.

19
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:58,520
This is...

20
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:01,600
This is the current Regent of Southern Ye,

21
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:02,710
Prince Qi.

22
00:01:03,110 --> 00:01:03,920
Prince Qi?

23
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,820
Never heard of him.

24
00:01:06,150 --> 00:01:08,920
Northern Qin cavalry
has fought Southern Ye for years.

25
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,520
We only know Young Lord Xiao.

26
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,270
It's fine.

27
00:01:12,890 --> 00:01:14,150
After the peace talks,

28
00:01:14,350 --> 00:01:16,120
you will naturally come to know me.

29
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:16,640
Please.

30
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,640
Hold on.

31
00:01:18,010 --> 00:01:20,830
Northern Qin and Southern Ye
have been at war for so many years.

32
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:22,830
Since we are having peace talks now,

33
00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:24,310
we, Northern Qin, must also show

34
00:01:24,310 --> 00:01:25,640
our sincerity for them.

35
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:27,840
I have specially prepared a gift

36
00:01:28,230 --> 00:01:29,230
for Southern Ye.

37
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:34,600
23 years ago, we captured your Capital,

38
00:01:35,080 --> 00:01:38,440
forcing the Southern Ye royal family
to flee south to Jiankang.

39
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,479
These are the royal descendants

40
00:01:39,479 --> 00:01:42,009
of Southern Ye
who couldn't escape back then.

41
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:43,150
For all these years, Qin

42
00:01:43,150 --> 00:01:45,680
has been feeding
and providing for them well.

43
00:01:45,940 --> 00:01:47,440
Since we are having peace talks,

44
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,640
we're sending them back

45
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,039
to reunite their family.

46
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:51,870
Wuyi, they are going too far.

47
00:01:53,110 --> 00:01:56,509
Northern Qin is also divided
into pro-war and pro-peace factions.

48
00:01:56,509 --> 00:01:59,509
The young Emperor wants peace,
but the Eagle King favors war.

49
00:01:59,509 --> 00:02:01,970
With the Eagle King
leading the delegation,

50
00:02:02,610 --> 00:02:04,400
the peace talks
will definitely not be easy.

51
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,330
Young Lord Xiao.

52
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:09,250
Your Highness, the Prince Qi.

53
00:02:09,310 --> 00:02:11,870
Can you see my sincerity?

54
00:02:14,070 --> 00:02:16,000
The Northern Qin people are going too far!

55
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,800
Stop them!

56
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,240
Stop them! Hurry, stop them!

57
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,680
Stop them!

58
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,400
This is too much!

59
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,840
Humiliating our people!

60
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,630
Stop them!

61
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:24,710
Yuanji.

62
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,570
You animals!

63
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,520
Eagle King.

64
00:02:31,370 --> 00:02:32,120
Please.

65
00:02:32,390 --> 00:02:33,190
Stop them!

66
00:03:59,270 --> 00:04:03,270
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

67
00:04:03,620 --> 00:04:06,170
[Episode 8]

68
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,590
The Northern Qin barbarians

69
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:08,530
[Honglu Temple]

70
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:08,960
humiliated our nation.

71
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,400
No peace talks!

72
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:12,080
The Northern Qin barbarians

73
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,410
humiliated our nation.

74
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:15,080
No peace talks!

75
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:18,140
Come on.

76
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:19,190
Let's go.

77
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,600
My Lady.

78
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,630
This is Honglu Temple.

79
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:28,480
We should probably go back.

80
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,830
The Eagle King
humiliated our royal family.

81
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:32,110
This is outrageous!

82
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,560
Didn't you hear what Yan Yue just said?

83
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,870
The students are filled
with righteous indignation

84
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:36,450
and have completely surrounded
the Honglu Temple,

85
00:04:36,450 --> 00:04:38,000
just waiting to charge in
and hack down the Eagle King.

86
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,130
Even Mao went there.

87
00:04:40,250 --> 00:04:41,210
But Xiao Wuyi

88
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,190
keeps the Beifu soldiers
confined to the camp,

89
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:44,850
not letting any news leak out.

90
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,880
What "bloodthirsty Yama Xiao"
are they talking about?

91
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:47,990
If something really happens,

92
00:04:47,990 --> 00:04:49,650
he'd only act tough around us.

93
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,720
So we must hurry in and help Mao.

94
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,500
We can't let him
be bullied by the Eagle King.

95
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,310
This...

96
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:02,160
What's wrong with your throat?

97
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:09,420
You secretly take the fire thunderstone.

98
00:05:09,420 --> 00:05:12,720
Do you want to go to the Honglu Temple
and blow up the Eagle King?

99
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,390
No, no.

100
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,050
I really didn't.

101
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:17,430
Stop. I'll tell you.

102
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:20,630
I heard that the Eagle King
coming for the peace talks

103
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:21,870
has a Longque Blade.

104
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,600
I want to see it.

105
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:24,800
I also want to see

106
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,240
how the legendary number
one blade in the world

107
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,360
is forged.

108
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,480
Know yourself and your enemy, right?

109
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,920
If only I could also forge

110
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:32,640
such a world-renowned, peerless weapon.

111
00:05:33,750 --> 00:05:35,830
Do I look stupid and easy to fool?

112
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:37,750
Really.

113
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,360
If I can actually forge it,

114
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,000
I'll give the first one to you.

115
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,000
The peace talks concern
the lifeblood of Ye.

116
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,430
If you dare to mess around...

117
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:44,630
Forget it if you don't believe me.

118
00:05:44,630 --> 00:05:45,510
So naggy.

119
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,070
You might as well tie me to your belt.

120
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:47,510
Okay.

121
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:59,190
Why did you skip the front door

122
00:05:59,190 --> 00:05:59,830
and fly up here?

123
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:01,600
If you're worried, go see for yourself.

124
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,120
The Northern Qin barbarians

125
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,450
humiliated our nation.

126
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:06,000
No peace talks!

127
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,360
They humiliated our nation.

128
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,680
No peace talks!

129
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:10,720
They humiliated our nation.

130
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,720
No peace talks!

131
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,510
This is Ye's territory.

132
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:15,750
Northern Qin lost the war.

133
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,560
They're the ones suing for peace now.

134
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:20,820
I don't believe he dares
to kill people in the capital of Ye!

135
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,560
Move away!

136
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,410
Move away!

137
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:25,720
Yizhi.

138
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,230
Your Highness Prince Qi.

139
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:30,330
You're finally here.

140
00:06:30,330 --> 00:06:32,490
Northern Qin humiliated our royal family.

141
00:06:32,490 --> 00:06:34,000
We were extremely angry upon hearing this.

142
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,260
If this can be tolerated, what cannot be?

143
00:06:36,310 --> 00:06:39,070
If the Eagle King doesn't
remove his crown and beg for forgiveness,

144
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:40,920
we will never agree to these peace talks!

145
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:44,159
We'll never agree!

146
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,480
What is this commotion?

147
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:48,140
Have you forgotten
what your master taught you?

148
00:06:48,190 --> 00:06:50,040
Students should
concentrate on their studies

149
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,630
and not discuss state affairs.

150
00:06:51,630 --> 00:06:52,870
Regarding this matter,

151
00:06:52,870 --> 00:06:55,360
I will discuss with Young Lord Xiao
to find a resolution.

152
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,270
You all leave first.

153
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:57,000
Your Highness.

154
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,870
Even the current regent
hosting the peace talks

155
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,130
is acting so cowardly.

156
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,430
Those Northern Qin bastards

157
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:02,600
have already walked all over us,

158
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,800
yet you still endure blindly.

159
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,630
Scholars neglect statecraft;
warriors neglect warfare.

160
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:06,750
Ye is doomed.

161
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:07,920
Nonsense!

162
00:07:08,110 --> 00:07:08,950
Throw!

163
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:13,070
No peace talks!

164
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,340
You said you came to see the blade.

165
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:31,720
But we can't just stand here and watch.

166
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,190
Are you this cowardly
on the battlefield, too?

167
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:34,120
How did you win your battles?

168
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:37,270
Do you think fighting a war is
just hacking at each other with blades?

169
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:39,090
Let me tell you the first rule
of the art of war.

170
00:07:39,090 --> 00:07:41,040
War is a matter
of vital importance to the state.

171
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:43,070
It is a matter of life and death,
a road either to safety or to ruin.

172
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:44,800
It must be thoroughly studied.

173
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,360
Stop!

174
00:07:48,450 --> 00:07:49,650
Move away! Move away!

175
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,370
Young Lord Xiao said

176
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,120
that peace talks are state policy

177
00:07:59,120 --> 00:07:59,920
and cannot be changed.

178
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,680
Considering that you are
young and hot-blooded,

179
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,280
and the future pillars of Ye,

180
00:08:03,310 --> 00:08:04,830
you will be lightly punished today
as a warning—

181
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:06,090
20 strokes of the cane.

182
00:08:06,430 --> 00:08:07,360
General Yan Yue,

183
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,830
this is inappropriate.

184
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:10,720
The students are acting out of patriotism.

185
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,870
It is exactly because His Highness
considers their patriotism

186
00:08:12,870 --> 00:08:14,270
that they are only getting 20 strokes.

187
00:08:14,270 --> 00:08:15,400
Under military law,

188
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,950
those who violate orders die.

189
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,870
Anyone else who misleads the public

190
00:08:19,870 --> 00:08:21,310
and disrupts the peace talks

191
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,600
will be executed without fail.

192
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,190
Hit!

193
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,190
What are you doing?

194
00:08:25,190 --> 00:08:25,950
How can you hit people?

195
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:27,680
Let go of me! What are you doing?

196
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,660
Xiao Wuyi, this...

197
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:32,030
Xiao Wuyi, how dare you hit me?

198
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,030
Yizhi, save me!

199
00:08:35,030 --> 00:08:36,440
He even dares to kill officials.

200
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:38,080
The Empress Dowager
can't even deal with him.

201
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,320
Why wouldn't he?

202
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:40,610
Your Highness,

203
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:42,549
His Highness asks you
to return to the Eastern Palace

204
00:08:42,549 --> 00:08:44,390
to continue drafting the peace treaty.

205
00:08:44,390 --> 00:08:45,850
Leave matters here to him.

206
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,550
Please.

207
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:54,910
Execute the punishment one by one.

208
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:55,510
Look,

209
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:57,270
isn't it solved?

210
00:08:58,430 --> 00:08:58,860
Hey.

211
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:01,390
Is this the solution you figured out?

212
00:09:01,390 --> 00:09:02,980
Those are Mao's classmates and friends,

213
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:04,580
and you just had them beaten?

214
00:09:04,750 --> 00:09:07,410
Xiao Wuyi, are you
that afraid of the Eagle King?

215
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,800
I really misjudged you.

216
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:16,200
Young Lord Xiao, His Highness,
the Eagle King, invites you.

217
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:19,870
Xiao Wuyi!

218
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,360
H-How do I get down?

219
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:24,630
If you still want to play
with fire in the future,

220
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:26,120
you must first learn how to run away.

221
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,120
What about today?

222
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,080
Figure it out yourself.

223
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,440
Figure...

224
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:32,360
You...

225
00:09:32,470 --> 00:09:32,840
I—

226
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,440
I...

227
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:35,360
I...

228
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,360
Speaking of mutton,

229
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:44,480
it's still the best
on Northern Qin grasslands.

230
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,910
It doesn't have any gamey smell.

231
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,170
Your Highness, try it.

232
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,010
Mu Lianyu,

233
00:09:51,820 --> 00:09:53,680
you don't want peace talks at all.

234
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,000
Your Highness tramples
on the people's will like this.

235
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:00,750
Aren't you afraid that the commoners
will hate the Beifu Army

236
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:01,600
and you?

237
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,660
The people's will can be used,

238
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,240
but cannot be fully trusted.

239
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:08,400
You went to great lengths
to provoke today's public anger.

240
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:10,100
You just hope that Ye will call off

241
00:10:10,100 --> 00:10:11,360
the peace talks first,

242
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,640
so you can answer to your little emperor

243
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,300
without taking the blame.

244
00:10:17,750 --> 00:10:19,390
I really didn't expect

245
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:22,030
that the decisive
Young Lord Xiao on the battlefield

246
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:24,870
would be so forbearing
off the battlefield.

247
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:28,510
It seems you're having
a hard time in Jiankang.

248
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,700
The feeling is mutual.

249
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:34,240
If it weren't for the heavy snow,

250
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,440
we wouldn't have lost

251
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:37,170
the battle at Jiuzhang Plain.

252
00:10:37,270 --> 00:10:38,360
In terms of archery and horsemanship,

253
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:40,550
our Northern Qin is far superior
to your Southern Ye.

254
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:41,790
But you lost.

255
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:45,030
Otherwise, I wouldn't be able
to eat

256
00:10:45,030 --> 00:10:46,950
Northern Qin's roasted mutton in Jiankang.

257
00:10:46,950 --> 00:10:47,550
Mu Lianyu.

258
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,120
Now your little emperor
also wants peace talks.

259
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,920
That's why you are sitting here.

260
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,510
Please stop your tricks.

261
00:10:53,510 --> 00:10:54,710
Don't try to anger me.

262
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,200
I can bear

263
00:10:59,110 --> 00:11:00,240
the people's anger.

264
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:10,720
Today, I have finally seen

265
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:13,360
your sincerity in the peace talks.

266
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,440
The most difficult part of the peace talks

267
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:18,040
is the ownership
of the three northern prefectures.

268
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:19,040
In that case,

269
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:21,920
why don't our countries

270
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:24,750
compete in public to determine

271
00:11:24,990 --> 00:11:25,990
their ownership?

272
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:31,210
I wonder if Southern Ye
dares to accept this challenge.

273
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:33,030
How do we compete?

274
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:35,780
Very simple.
Shoot the willow on horseback—

275
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,570
a game of life and death.

276
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,560
Do you dare to accept?

277
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,970
Shoot the willow on horseback.

278
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,960
Each country will send three people
and three horses,

279
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,200
with three arrows per person.

280
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,600
When all arrows are shot,

281
00:11:53,730 --> 00:11:56,150
whichever country
has more arrows left on the target

282
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:58,280
gets the three northern prefectures.

283
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,240
Your Majesty, the Empress Dowager,
these three prefectures

284
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,790
were originally the territory of Ye.

285
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:05,320
It's the Qin people
who have been invading us.

286
00:12:05,390 --> 00:12:07,150
How can we use such a child's play

287
00:12:07,150 --> 00:12:09,680
to determine the ownership
of our territory?

288
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:12,360
Young Lord Xiao, what do you think?

289
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,550
He proposed this competition

290
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:20,870
simply because he doesn't
want peace talks

291
00:12:20,870 --> 00:12:22,600
and wants to force us to refuse.

292
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:23,720
Even if we agree,

293
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:26,960
he just wants to use this competition
to win back their pride.

294
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:27,840
In that case,

295
00:12:28,670 --> 00:12:29,960
we shall fight again

296
00:12:30,630 --> 00:12:32,470
and make him admit defeat.

297
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,670
Can you guarantee a sure win,
Your Highness?

298
00:12:36,670 --> 00:12:38,200
Matters on the battlefield

299
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,720
can never be guaranteed.

300
00:12:41,910 --> 00:12:43,510
Even you can't guarantee it.

301
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,240
If we win this battle,

302
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,990
we might finally hold our heads high.

303
00:12:46,990 --> 00:12:48,050
But what if we lose?

304
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:50,320
Your Highness and the Beifu Army
will be ruined.

305
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:52,480
The three northern prefectures
will fall into the hands of the Qin.

306
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,870
The advantage of our
peace talks with Northern Qin

307
00:12:53,870 --> 00:12:55,080
will also be gone.

308
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,380
Have you considered this, Young Lord Xiao?

309
00:12:56,380 --> 00:12:58,180
If every battle were a sure win,

310
00:12:58,570 --> 00:13:00,500
there would be no war in this world.

311
00:13:03,370 --> 00:13:04,290
Let us fight.

312
00:13:05,390 --> 00:13:06,150
Let the people and scholars

313
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:08,000
who are criticizing me see

314
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:09,600
that the peace talks I led

315
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:11,120
were for the future of Ye,

316
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,640
not because I feared war.

317
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:24,240
I am willing to fight Northern Qin!

318
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:31,560
Wuyi.

319
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,120
Wuyi.

320
00:13:35,010 --> 00:13:36,200
Northern Qin
was founded on military might.

321
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,240
Their people excel
in archery and horsemanship.

322
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,150
Are you really confident?

323
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:39,910
Yizhi, why not think
about it the other way around?

324
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:41,750
If Northern Qin
loses even the horse archery

325
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:42,910
they are most proud of to us,

326
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:44,840
and loses three prefectures
because of it,

327
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,050
what will happen within Northern Qin?

328
00:13:46,050 --> 00:13:47,080
Their morale will plummet.

329
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,630
But that's easier said than done.

330
00:13:48,630 --> 00:13:49,510
In this archery competition,

331
00:13:49,510 --> 00:13:50,630
arrows can not only shoot targets,

332
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:51,960
but also people and horses.

333
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:52,720
In the arena,

334
00:13:53,270 --> 00:13:54,630
the Eagle King will definitely
use lethal moves against you.

335
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:55,600
Then let's see if he has

336
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,200
what it takes to take my life.

337
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:01,790
Yizhi.

338
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:08,020
I'm sorry about what happened

339
00:14:09,820 --> 00:14:11,620
at the Honglu Temple yesterday.

340
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,440
I had no choice.

341
00:14:15,030 --> 00:14:16,560
You don't need to say this to me.

342
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:17,820
I believe in you, Wuyi.

343
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:21,150
But for the peace talks,

344
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:22,840
what is your bottom line?

345
00:14:24,390 --> 00:14:25,120
Time.

346
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:26,510
Time?

347
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:28,030
Conditions are not important,

348
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:30,480
but the reform of the Beifu
needs at least three years of peace.

349
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:32,030
I am confident that after the reform,

350
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:33,720
I can increase
the Beifu Army's combat power by 80%.

351
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:34,720
As long as I have time,

352
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:37,030
the Northern Expedition
will definitely succeed.

353
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:38,490
So no matter what happens,

354
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:40,000
no matter what tricks the Eagle King

355
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:40,870
has waiting for me,

356
00:14:40,870 --> 00:14:42,930
I must make the peace talks a success.

357
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,000
Wuyi,

358
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:46,910
I really envy
your boldness and determination.

359
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:47,960
Ye can lose three prefectures,

360
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:50,150
but we absolutely cannot lose you,
Xiao Wuyi.

361
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:51,600
Losing three prefectures
is a temporary loss.

362
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:54,260
Losing Wuyi means
losing the nation's destiny.

363
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,270
In the arena,

364
00:14:55,550 --> 00:14:56,550
you must be very careful.

365
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:57,480
Li Yizhi,

366
00:14:58,050 --> 00:14:59,890
since when did you become
so good at flattering?

367
00:14:59,890 --> 00:15:02,150
I'm speaking from the bottom of my heart.

368
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:04,000
You don't know how much I envy you

369
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:06,530
for building your career
with your own hands.

370
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:11,750
Wuyi.

371
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:14,590
Do you want me to stay?

372
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,480
Do you think I, Li Yizhi,

373
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,460
am worthy of being the Crown Prince of Ye?

374
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,120
I didn't expect you, Xiao Wuyi,

375
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,120
to be speechless.

376
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,260
Never mind. I was just asking.

377
00:15:36,290 --> 00:15:37,600
Don't take it seriously.

378
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:38,910
Jiayu doesn't like the palace.

379
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:39,720
Even for her sake,

380
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:40,630
I can't stay.

381
00:15:41,130 --> 00:15:41,730
By the way,

382
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,360
the hawthorn cakes she made last time

383
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,490
tasted really good.

384
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:45,790
I am not used to the food in the palace.

385
00:15:45,790 --> 00:15:47,240
I rely entirely on them
to whet my appetite.

386
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,390
Could I trouble you

387
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:50,980
to ask her to make some more for me?

388
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:52,750
I got it.

389
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:07,670
Later, let's give all the medicinal herbs

390
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:09,070
we brought today to them.

391
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:12,620
I'll go take a look over there.

392
00:16:18,630 --> 00:16:23,810
Master. Master. Master.

393
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,960
I told you to study behind closed doors

394
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,670
and not discuss state affairs.

395
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:28,580
What about you?

396
00:16:28,850 --> 00:16:30,850
Did you even listen to me?

397
00:16:32,150 --> 00:16:34,280
Do not get involved in the peace talks.

398
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:36,670
I am getting old

399
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:39,660
and don't have many days
left to protect you.

400
00:16:39,990 --> 00:16:41,160
Please don't

401
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:43,550
cause any more trouble blindly,

402
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:44,440
okay?

403
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:45,320
Master.

404
00:16:46,670 --> 00:16:48,670
It's not that we are acting blindly.

405
00:16:49,030 --> 00:16:51,360
The Northern Qin people
have gone too far.

406
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:53,030
We study the books of the sages.

407
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:54,240
How could we just sit by and watch?

408
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:55,040
Today's blood

409
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:56,510
is not to cause trouble,

410
00:16:56,510 --> 00:16:57,600
but to wake the people.

411
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:58,750
And Xiao Wuyi,

412
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,720
as the commander of the Beifu Army,

413
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:01,480
to fear the enemy

414
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:03,030
and abandon the people like this
just for peace talks

415
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:04,400
is an absolute disgrace!

416
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:05,240
Exactly.

417
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:06,680
Enough.

418
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:14,960
Has your mother sent you any messages?

419
00:17:17,210 --> 00:17:19,170
Shouldn't she be at home?

420
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:22,750
Yaoyao,

421
00:17:24,349 --> 00:17:26,790
I am your father.

422
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:31,200
You've never been good at lying.

423
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,680
Your mother divorced me.

424
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:35,620
She wouldn't keep it from you.

425
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:39,350
She did leave a letter.

426
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:41,030
She said all these years,

427
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:43,510
trapped in Jiankang Palace
and the Grand Tutor's Mansion,

428
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:44,710
she was very unhappy.

429
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:46,030
Now that I'm married,

430
00:17:46,830 --> 00:17:48,630
she can finally follow her heart

431
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,490
and live the life she wants.

432
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,200
She also said

433
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:54,200
the divorce is between you two.

434
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,460
She is still my mother,

435
00:17:58,420 --> 00:17:59,950
and you are still my father.

436
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:02,030
That's all she said.

437
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:04,480
Even if I knew where she went,

438
00:18:04,750 --> 00:18:05,880
I wouldn't tell you.

439
00:18:09,150 --> 00:18:10,550
If there's nothing else,

440
00:18:11,070 --> 00:18:12,070
I will leave now.

441
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,960
For this round of peace talks,

442
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:17,820
a Northern Qin official proposed

443
00:18:18,270 --> 00:18:21,030
to send a royal daughter
to marry into Northern Qin.

444
00:18:21,030 --> 00:18:22,590
Who do you think

445
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:25,790
is the most suitable
among the Jiankang royals now?

446
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:29,240
Li Lejun.

447
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:32,550
You want to send Lejun away
for a political marriage?

448
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:33,750
It's not us.

449
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:37,070
It's Xiao Wuyi.

450
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:39,070
Looking at his current actions,

451
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:41,960
you can tell he will definitely
make sure the peace talks succeed,

452
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:43,550
no matter what it takes.

453
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:47,030
Everyone knows
the miserable and maddened state

454
00:18:47,030 --> 00:18:48,270
of the Southern Ye royal clan

455
00:18:48,270 --> 00:18:51,200
inside the iron cage outside
the city gates that day.

456
00:18:51,350 --> 00:18:55,280
You surely wouldn't want Princess Pingning
to suffer such a disaster,

457
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:56,000
right?

458
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:59,270
If you want to protect her...

459
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,160
I

460
00:19:06,070 --> 00:19:07,510
can help.

461
00:19:09,580 --> 00:19:10,580
What's the price?

462
00:19:11,250 --> 00:19:11,810
Father,

463
00:19:13,290 --> 00:19:15,020
what do you want me to do for you?

464
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:17,720
The peace talks may succeed,

465
00:19:18,490 --> 00:19:19,640
but Xiao Wuyi

466
00:19:22,380 --> 00:19:23,200
must lose.

467
00:19:28,890 --> 00:19:29,480
Lose?

468
00:19:32,790 --> 00:19:34,920
Coincidentally, the bone is injured.

469
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:38,100
You must give him
the medicine on time, as I said.

470
00:19:44,480 --> 00:19:45,310
Pei Runheng?

471
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:48,070
Wake up.

472
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:49,400
Doctor.

473
00:19:50,550 --> 00:19:51,410
Your Highness.

474
00:19:51,550 --> 00:19:52,440
Do you know him?

475
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:55,070
He is badly injured.

476
00:19:55,550 --> 00:19:56,920
Doctor, come here.

477
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,400
Wake up. Wake up.

478
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:13,700
The noble clans are committing treason.

479
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:15,960
They are parasites of the state.

480
00:20:18,270 --> 00:20:18,920
Runheng.

481
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:20,420
-Who is Runheng?
-You—

482
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,000
Go away.

483
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:23,860
Don't touch me.

484
00:20:31,110 --> 00:20:33,680
Do you know that scholar?

485
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:38,650
I mistook him for someone else.

486
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:42,110
He looks a lot like an old friend of mine.

487
00:20:42,920 --> 00:20:45,270
Runheng would never look at me

488
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:47,880
with such unfamiliarity and disgust.

489
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:48,550
Besides,

490
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:50,720
I saw Runheng's body.

491
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:54,550
Mr. Runheng was your sweetheart?

492
00:20:58,310 --> 00:20:59,920
On the day of the Double Ninth Ceremony,

493
00:20:59,920 --> 00:21:01,030
I saw the prayer tablet you wrote

494
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:02,480
on the prayer tree.

495
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:04,240
That name was on it.

496
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:07,860
But I didn't expect
that he had already passed away.

497
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,640
The prayer tree
on the Double Ninth Festival

498
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:11,400
is also called the Yin-Yang Tree.

499
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:14,400
It was originally meant to commemorate
friendship with the deceased.

500
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:15,110
What?

501
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:17,180
Then Ruisheng also...

502
00:21:20,110 --> 00:21:23,030
So you married Xiao Wuyi

503
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:25,200
because your sweetheart was gone?

504
00:21:27,030 --> 00:21:28,880
It was because
I was going to marry Xiao Wuyi

505
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:29,960
I beg Your Majesty, Empress Dowager
for mercy,

506
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:30,960
that he was gone.

507
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,160
I'm already engaged.

508
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:38,830
His Majesty has just ascended the throne,

509
00:21:38,830 --> 00:21:40,310
and his position is still unstable.

510
00:21:40,310 --> 00:21:42,370
And the Beifu Army needs provisions.

511
00:21:43,030 --> 00:21:45,550
Now is a good time
for the He family and the Xiao family

512
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:47,150
to form a marriage alliance.

513
00:21:48,110 --> 00:21:50,570
If you weren't the only eligible
in the clan,

514
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:52,120
I would never force you.

515
00:21:53,350 --> 00:21:53,960
Aunt.

516
00:21:55,070 --> 00:21:55,830
Aunt.

517
00:21:59,250 --> 00:22:01,510
And I made the most regrettable decision

518
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,750
in my life.

519
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,110
What was it?

520
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:10,110
I told my parents and the Empress Dowager

521
00:22:10,110 --> 00:22:11,880
that I already had a sweetheart,

522
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:13,740
letting them know about Runheng.

523
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:16,640
Runheng was the son
of the academy's headmaster

524
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:19,170
and a distant relative
of my mother's family.

525
00:22:19,270 --> 00:22:21,200
I thought my parents would help me.

526
00:22:21,590 --> 00:22:22,720
But not long after,

527
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:24,070
what I received

528
00:22:25,550 --> 00:22:27,480
was actually the news of his death.

529
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:30,310
Later, I found out

530
00:22:30,310 --> 00:22:32,750
that the border military situation
was urgent at that time,

531
00:22:32,750 --> 00:22:35,200
and the Beifu Army urgently needed
the He family's provision of support.

532
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:37,550
Because I kept refusing
to agree to the marriage,

533
00:22:37,550 --> 00:22:39,720
the forces of the Empress Dowager
and the Heir

534
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:41,320
had both gone to look for him.

535
00:22:41,370 --> 00:22:44,760
So someone murdered your sweetheart?

536
00:22:46,510 --> 00:22:47,830
It might be Xiao Wuyi?

537
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:52,550
Or it might be the Empress Dowager.

538
00:22:52,550 --> 00:22:54,210
But if Xiao Wuyi really did it,

539
00:22:54,830 --> 00:22:57,240
don't you hate him?

540
00:22:57,790 --> 00:22:58,650
In that battle,

541
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:00,730
Xiao Wuyi won beautifully.

542
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:02,310
He completely recaptured

543
00:23:02,310 --> 00:23:04,310
the Yushan Pass, which was lost
for nearly 20 years,

544
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:05,910
and is my family's hometown.

545
00:23:06,960 --> 00:23:10,090
Tens of thousands of people returned
to their homeland.

546
00:23:10,930 --> 00:23:13,890
You tell me,
how am I supposed to hate him?

547
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:16,160
Since then, I told myself

548
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:17,710
to stop investigating.

549
00:23:17,710 --> 00:23:19,440
Even if it really was Xiao Wuyi,

550
00:23:20,750 --> 00:23:22,920
I would still be Heir's Consort.

551
