And Anmin,

819
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,030
he still doesn't know

820
00:35:07,740 --> 00:35:10,230
that it's you who doesn't want him
to return to the Northern Border

821
00:35:10,230 --> 00:35:11,890
and on the battlefield again.

822
00:35:13,550 --> 00:35:15,960
So he has taken all his resentment
over the years

823
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:17,070
out on Wuyi.

824
00:35:18,230 --> 00:35:20,840
Fortunately, they are both tough
on the outside but warm on the inside.

825
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:23,170
But if this misunderstanding continues,

826
00:35:24,060 --> 00:35:26,790
it will sooner or later turn
into real animosity.

827
00:35:36,030 --> 00:35:36,760
Darling,

828
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:41,550
do you really want to see

829
00:35:41,550 --> 00:35:43,810
the two brothers at odds with each other?

830
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:01,320
Anmin wants to return
to the Northern Border.

831
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:02,050
That's good.

832
00:36:02,630 --> 00:36:04,630
Currently, the Beifu camps
are still short of organization.

833
00:36:04,630 --> 00:36:06,430
He has the talent to lead troops.

834
00:36:06,710 --> 00:36:08,170
If he is willing to return,

835
00:36:08,230 --> 00:36:11,690
your pressure on the western front
next year will be lessened.

836
00:36:12,590 --> 00:36:14,050
You are absolutely right.

837
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:20,240
Quickly write to your mother and
tell Anmin to return to the battlefield.

838
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:28,760
Young Master Yao.

839
00:36:29,150 --> 00:36:29,950
Don't help me.

840
00:36:34,680 --> 00:36:35,790
Stop practicing.

841
00:36:36,110 --> 00:36:38,370
Your leg can't take this kind of torment.

842
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:40,510
Do you also think I'm useless?

843
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,240
Even though I can't ride a horse,

844
00:36:42,240 --> 00:36:43,070
my archery

845
00:36:43,590 --> 00:36:44,920
and close combat skills

846
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:46,980
are no worse than Xiao Wuyi's.

847
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:50,070
He learned wrestling from me back then.

848
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:52,230
On what grounds
does he stop me from competing?

849
00:36:52,230 --> 00:36:53,830
I'm worried about your legs.

850
00:36:54,590 --> 00:36:56,190
My father doesn't care about me.

851
00:36:56,190 --> 00:36:57,920
My younger brother looks down on me.

852
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:58,840
Do you also...

853
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:11,000
Prepare more medicine for bruises
and injuries for Young Master Yao.

854
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:11,550
Yes.

855
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:52,840
Nanxing.

856
00:37:53,630 --> 00:37:55,840
Don't you think this room is very stuffy?

857
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:56,840
It's like a prison.

858
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:57,960
It's only been two days,

859
00:37:57,960 --> 00:37:59,320
and you can't stay still anymore.

860
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,710
Just like at home before,

861
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:02,030
you always want to run outside.

862
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,880
Her Highness couldn't control you.

863
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:04,940
If this is a prison,

864
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:07,780
it's the most wonderful prison
in the world.

865
00:38:09,710 --> 00:38:12,280
These are the recent requests
on Miraculous Craft.

866
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,110
Take a look

867
00:38:13,110 --> 00:38:14,150
and see if there are
any mechanical gadgets

868
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:15,550
that you're interested.

869
00:38:15,630 --> 00:38:17,440
You can make some to pass the time.

870
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,590
The competition is in a few days.

871
00:38:18,590 --> 00:38:19,840
It will pass.

872
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:23,280
A wooden kite
that can carry a person and fly.

873
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,960
An arrow that bends its path
to pursue prey.

874
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:26,880
Fire oil that cannot
be extinguished by water.

875
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:28,110
And the buyers' names...

876
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:29,130
Red Dragon, Black Dragon,

877
00:38:29,130 --> 00:38:30,530
Black Dragon, Full Moon.

878
00:38:31,230 --> 00:38:33,320
Isn't it obvious
they are Qing Long and Yan Yue?

879
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:37,050
This must be Xiao Wuyi sending them
to make things difficult for me.

880
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:40,070
So boring.

881
00:38:42,670 --> 00:38:43,960
Someone!

882
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:44,960
Is anybody there?

883
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:56,850
Let's go!

884
00:39:01,150 --> 00:39:02,760
The fire thunderstone of the Beifu Army

885
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:04,360
is truly all bark and no bite.

886
00:39:04,590 --> 00:39:05,920
I don't know who designed them.

887
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:07,320
They just wasted my time.

888
00:39:07,860 --> 00:39:08,860
I have to use mine.

889
00:39:20,710 --> 00:39:21,590
I'm a genius.

890
00:39:30,030 --> 00:39:30,630
Ghost!

891
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:33,500
[Yuan Xiaole]

892
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:33,930
Are you really Li Yunzhao's daughter?

893
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:37,110
You don't look much like her.

894
00:39:37,550 --> 00:39:38,950
But you have some skills.

895
00:39:39,800 --> 00:39:41,630
I have to say,

896
00:39:41,800 --> 00:39:43,670
after you modified this fire thunderstone,

897
00:39:43,670 --> 00:39:45,270
its power actually increased quite a bit.

898
00:39:45,270 --> 00:39:47,000
How much saltpeter did you use?

899
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:48,440
Hey, who are you?

900
00:39:48,510 --> 00:39:49,440
Do I know you?

901
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:50,810
Move. I'm going out.

902
00:39:52,540 --> 00:39:53,340
Wait a minute.

903
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:56,450
Xiao Wuyi really didn't lie to me.

904
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:58,090
You do have some talent.

905
00:39:58,330 --> 00:39:59,320
I'm definitely taking you

906
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:00,320
as my apprentice.

907
00:40:00,860 --> 00:40:03,050
Let me show you my fire thunderstone.

908
00:40:03,110 --> 00:40:04,840
Its power is no less than yours.

909
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:09,380
Let's exchange our thoughts on this.

910
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:12,510
Who said I'm going to be your apprentice?

911
00:40:12,510 --> 00:40:14,310
Are you drunk in broad daylight?

912
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:18,180
Your temper is quite like your mother's.

913
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:20,570
How could you possibly know my mother?

914
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:22,920
Not only do I know her,

915
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:25,420
but we fought a lot when we were young.

916
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,810
Let me tell you a secret.

917
00:40:27,440 --> 00:40:29,700
Your mother doesn't have much time left.

918
00:40:31,550 --> 00:40:33,030
What did you say?

919
00:40:33,030 --> 00:40:33,760
Listen.

920
00:40:33,760 --> 00:40:35,310
Don't use seniority to boss me around.

921
00:40:35,310 --> 00:40:37,420
You designed this fire thunderstone?

922
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:39,080
The design is truly terrible.

923
00:40:40,150 --> 00:40:41,810
What's wrong with it? Tell me.

924
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:42,960
It's too big.

925
00:40:42,960 --> 00:40:45,420
Do you know
what "all bark and no bite" means?

926
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:47,070
What do you know?

927
00:40:47,150 --> 00:40:47,800
Big?

928
00:40:48,510 --> 00:40:49,510
Its power is huge!

929
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:52,110
The ones I design,
even if they are only this small,

930
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:53,770
are more powerful than yours.

931
00:40:55,260 --> 00:40:55,920
Okay, okay.

932
00:40:56,550 --> 00:40:58,280
W-We'll talk about this later.

933
00:40:58,660 --> 00:40:59,520
Let me tell you.

934
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:02,710
I've never been wrong in fortune-telling.

935
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:06,070
Not only did I figure out that your mother
doesn't have much time left,

936
00:41:06,070 --> 00:41:09,230
but I also figured out
you will marry twice,

937
00:41:10,160 --> 00:41:11,920
no, three times in your life.

938
00:41:12,720 --> 00:41:14,800
And your husband, he'll die young.

939
00:41:16,230 --> 00:41:16,880
Is that so?

940
00:41:18,670 --> 00:41:19,880
Nanxing, get him!

941
00:41:21,190 --> 00:41:23,000
Who are you saying
doesn't have much time left?

942
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:26,260
-Watch out for the fire thunderstone
-Who are you cursing?

943
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:38,630
Why are you glaring at me?

944
00:41:38,630 --> 00:41:39,760
I told you to watch out
for the fire thunderstone.

945
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:41,820
Watch out for the fire thunderstone.

946
00:41:44,030 --> 00:41:45,560
Qing Long, long time no see.

947
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:46,740
Did you miss me?

948
00:41:53,310 --> 00:41:54,430
Give it back to me.

949
00:41:55,710 --> 00:41:57,630
You know how to make stirrups, too?

950
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:58,280
At first glance,

951
00:41:58,280 --> 00:42:00,480
I knew this was designed for Xiao Yao.

952
00:42:01,070 --> 00:42:01,920
Xiao Wuyi

953
00:42:01,920 --> 00:42:03,670
asked me to design one before, too.

954
00:42:03,670 --> 00:42:04,620
My design

955
00:42:06,070 --> 00:42:07,530
was much better than this.

956
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:10,840
You designed one for him, too?

957
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:11,630
When?

958
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:13,760
A long time ago.

959
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:19,150
It was probably right
after Xiao Yao got injured.

960
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:22,000
Xiao Wuyi was worried his brother

961
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:23,930
couldn't get over his disability.

962
00:42:25,150 --> 00:42:25,880
It was a pity.

963
00:42:26,760 --> 00:42:28,970
He told me to stop
when the blueprint was only half done.

964
00:42:28,970 --> 00:42:29,820
Why stop?

965
00:42:30,670 --> 00:42:32,070
Naturally, it's because someone

966
00:42:32,070 --> 00:42:35,600
didn't want Xiao Yao to ride a horse
onto the battlefield again.

967
00:42:38,190 --> 00:42:38,840
Kiddo.

968
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:41,710
You are quite talented

969
00:42:41,710 --> 00:42:42,630
in alchemy and metalworking,

970
00:42:42,630 --> 00:42:45,440
but your structural design
still lacks a bit.

971
00:42:47,410 --> 00:42:48,400
It's my blueprint. You...

972
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:49,280
Hold on.

973
00:42:52,510 --> 00:42:53,000
Look.

974
00:42:54,840 --> 00:42:56,440
If it's connected like this,

975
00:42:56,630 --> 00:42:58,100
and then attached to the saddle,

976
00:42:58,100 --> 00:42:59,820
wouldn't it be much more flexible?

977
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:00,850
The biggest problem with your design

978
00:43:00,850 --> 00:43:02,710
is that it's not flexible enough.

979
00:43:03,030 --> 00:43:04,150
It works fine with light pressure,

980
00:43:04,150 --> 00:43:06,360
but once too much force is applied,
it creates drag

981
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:08,150
and can throw the rider off,

982
00:43:08,150 --> 00:43:09,840
leaving them vulnerable
to being trampled by their own horse.

983
00:43:09,840 --> 00:43:10,840
Wait, wait, wait.

984
00:43:11,070 --> 00:43:13,480
Did you say applying force
causes dragging?

985
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:14,030
Oh, no.

986
00:43:14,320 --> 00:43:16,060
His Highness is testing the stirrups
for Young Master Yao.

987
00:43:16,060 --> 00:43:16,710
What?

988
00:43:56,110 --> 00:43:57,590
Why is it blurry again?

